==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Piercing
<hw>Pier"cing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Forcibly entering,
or adapted to enter, at or by a point; perforating; penetrating; keen;
-- used also figuratively; <as>as, a <ex>piercing</ex> instrument, or
thrust</as>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Piercing</xex> eloquence.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Pier"cing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Pier"cing*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pierian</ent>⟦br⟧
